# Google OAuth — used by telefonista users to send email from their own Gmail
# 1. Create OAuth client in Google Cloud Console (type: Web application)
# 2. Authorized redirect URI must match GOOGLE_OAUTH_REDIRECT_URL exactly
# 3. Enable Gmail API and add scope https://www.googleapis.com/auth/gmail.send
# 4. GOOGLE_TOKEN_ENC_KEY: 32 random bytes hex-encoded (64 chars)
#    Generate with: openssl rand -hex 32
